## AMATEUR RADIO USE

This Software is designed for use by licensed amateur radio operators. Users must:

1. Hold a valid amateur radio license for their jurisdiction
2. Comply with all applicable amateur radio regulations
3. Identify transmissions with their assigned callsign as required by law
